title: Interview with a Billionaire
itunes:title: Interview with a Billionaire
description:
Episode 581 - Jeff Hoffman is a billionaire. That's alone makes this episode interesting, but what makes it even more amazing is the value that Jeff brings to this episode. He teaches you the mindset to become a billionaire and also how strategies that he uses to come up with ideas that no one has ever thought of. Jeff is an amazing human and I can't wait for you to hear this episode!
